tilities — consumed by the engine and phases.\n\n| Module | Path | Responsibility | Status |\n| --- | --- | --- | --- |\n| Types | `src/types.ts` | Central type definitions: all shared interfaces and type aliases used across the codebase. | `todo` |\n| config | `src/config.ts` | Loads and merges `.super-ralph/config.toml` with defaults; resolves AI model selection by bead labels or CLI override. | `todo` |\n| Template | `src/template.ts` | Loads and renders Handlebars `.hbs` prompt templates stored in `.super-ralph/`. | `todo` |\n| Output parser | `src/output-parser.ts` | Accumulates raw SSE event lines and display text during a session; caps total size at 250,000 characters. | `todo` |\n| Run state | `src/run-state.ts` | Persists per-run artifacts: timestamped run directory, live `session.json`, JSONL event log, and per-iteration transcripts. | `todo` |\n| Run status | `src/run-status.ts` | Read-only companion to run state; resolves a run reference and reads back session state, event counts, and transcript paths. | `todo` |\n| Progress | `src/progress.ts` | Appends human-readable Markdown progress entries to `progress.md` after each iteration; reads recent entries back for agent context. | `todo` |\n| Skills | `src/skills.ts` | Resolves a skill name or file path to its Markdown content; supports built-in skills and arbitrary user-supplied paths. | `todo` |\n| Timeout | `src/timeout.ts` | Races a promise against a deadline; rejects with a custom error message if the timeout elapses first. | `todo` |\n| Init | `src/init.ts` | Scaffolds a new project: creates `.super-ralph/`, copies templates, writes `config.toml`, installs the OpenCode plugin, and runs `br init`. | `todo` |\n| Events | `src/events.ts` | Defines the engine event union type, a lightweight pub/sub emitter, and a default console renderer for terminal output. | `todo` |\n\n---\n\n## CLI Entry Point\n\n| Module | Path | Responsibility | Status |\n| --- | --- | --- | --- |\n| Index | `src/index.ts` | CLI en